{"tid":89993,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥帥認輸：已和冠軍說再見","createTime":"2017-01-21T17:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T17:22:14.000Z","uid":172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c472b8930ce38e508bae813926c65cfd57d382c7","tid":89993,"uid":172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4WN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0acadaa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼城在周六英超將主場迎戰熱刺，爆發前列大戰，但領隊哥迪奧拿在賽前卻先認低威，自言已和冠軍說了再見。<br />\n<br />\n曼城近期戰績再次陷入低迷，在上輪英超被愛華頓以4:0大炒後，現僅以42分排第5，和榜首車路士相差10分，與次席的熱刺則相差3分。要是周六一戰不敵熱刺，「藍月」要後上奪標可說是困難重重。<br />\n<br />\n大戰當前，曼城主帥哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）沒有為球員和球迷注下強心針之餘，更大潑冷水，他表示：「我們已經和冠軍說了再見。我預計今場對熱刺，將會和首循環一樣。」在該仗，熱刺主場以2:0取勝。<br />\n<br />\n哥帥坦言，因為熱刺是英超其中一支最強的球隊：「他們的主宰球賽的能力非常高，和車路士有點相似，但球員走動更快，而且十分清楚隊友的位置，可以在很微細的空間有高質素的傳球。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af85b54f96dd7646618b6e222c51f5e8770aa3bc","tid":89993,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25b0b3ca3d1c00975410f77e3337396816f5112f","tid":89993,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"認低威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你即刻補番一萬蚊曼城先"},{"pid":"704a4a676eaedde940e4cb516e474850238c8992","tid":89993,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:17:04.000Z","msg":"以為輸撚左唔洗比人屌?我祝你年年有今日呀死哥狗"},{"pid":"e6ad64f7b5dbc68821288b0b4ded50af8ce8eeb5","tid":89993,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"feel到鏝會由呢場開始不敗"},{"pid":"d843d6c13e95aa89779538479fc05a76058f7a34","tid":89993,"uid":172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認低威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你即刻補番一萬蚊曼城先</blockquote><br />\n岩岩補左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  準備約經紀睇樓"},{"pid":"7a294b2217e4eca83ee0880ee6c8c0cf51c56956","tid":89993,"uid":16135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認低威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你即刻補番一萬蚊曼城先</blockquote><br />\n岩岩補左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  準備約經紀睇樓</blockquote><br />\n輸咗我笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2601051713093929c3d97938e408137ccd50a5","tid":89993,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"曼城需要輸番一場"}]}